GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_SolutionArchetypes> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_SolutionArchetypes> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#SolutionArchetypes> ;
    narr:childCount "33"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers the **solution archetypes** aswritten sells against — demo scripts, use-case taxonomies, and live deal playbooks. The cleanest three-way frame is the use-case trio: [governing a human team](narr:Narrative_UseCase1GoverningHumanTeam) (ARB, leadership), [agentic steering](narr:Narrative_UseCase2AgenticSteering) at one-model and whole-ecosystem scale, and [steering the shared process across engagements](narr:Narrative_UseCase3SharedProcessSteering) (20260526). A parallel [collaboration-shape taxonomy](narr:Narrative_CollaborationTaxonomy) (Individual→Self/Team/Many, Team→Many) is flagged as missing from the strategy doc. Concrete demos cluster around the enterprise customer: [QA onboarding](narr:SolutionArchetype_QAOnboarding) (the customer's chief architect's 'killer sales demo'), [CEO knowledge transfer](narr:SolutionArchetype_CEOKnowledgeTransfer), [code quality through business context](narr:SolutionArchetype_CodeQualityThroughContext), and the 60-second [YC value-loop flow](narr:Archetype_YCDemoFlow). The [ARB pilot](narr:Narrative_EnterpriseCustomerARBPilotUseCase) ('have an AI replace me at ARB') became a [three-phase POC→Pilot→Scale proposal](narr:Narrative_EnterpriseCustomerEngagementProposal) (20260414), backed by sales-motion claims: [sponsor≠champion](narr:Narrative_SponsorVsChampionPlaybook) and [POC/MSA in parallel](narr:Narrative_POCMSAParallelism) (Tony, 20260421). Consulting reframes the [deck as derived artifact](narr:Narrative_ConsultingModuleDeliverable); [extraction scope](narr:Narrative_ExtractionScopeOrgWorldview) reframes 'domain' as organizational worldview (20260317). Healthcare adds the [proposal artifact](narr:Narrative_ProposalArtifactPractitioner) lock-in (20260430).""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Archetype_YCDemoFlow> ;
